25f405f3-ed2e-4c63-9986-8f8149767e4f.user_question: what is the difference between alm octane and qc

suggestible_questions.question: Is ALM Octane and QC same?
suggestible_questions.answer: HP ALM is a software that is designed to manage the various phases of Software Development Life Cycle(SDLC) right from requirements gathering to testing. Earlier, it was known as HP Quality Center (QC). ... HP QC is named as HP ALM from version 11.0
